1. Highlevel steps of DB upgrade :

=> PRECHECKS/:
-------------------

check invalid object
Recyclbin purge
backup
store gather
install 12c binaries
Genarate AWR (12c)
Freshly bounce database (shu immediate / init 6 to restart)
change required parameter.

=> UPGRADE/:
------------------
Install sample config file
changes in config file
Use modes - analyze - Fixup - Diploy using autoupgrade.jar utility tool.

=> POSTCHECK/:
----------------------
check DB version
check the time zone
check the invalid objects
change compatible parameters
-------------------------------------- End of upgrade high level steps   ---------------------------------------

